{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d0a6c85e-64dc-437f-ac5c-050ea3749632", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a6c85e-64dc-437f-ac5c-050ea3749632@2.pkg/1772602430728/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602431721", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a6c85e-64dc-437f-ac5c-050ea3749632@2.pkg/1772602430728/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602431721"}, "identifier": "d0a6c85e-64dc-437f-ac5c-050ea3749632", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】诗不是要挣脱春天，而是挽留春天。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​饮酒</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​晋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>陶渊明</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>结庐在人境，而无车马喧。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>问君何能尔？心远地自偏。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>采菊东篱下，悠然见南山。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>山气日夕佳，飞鸟相与还。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>此中有真意，欲辨已忘言。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​​春日即事</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>宋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>​李弥逊</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>小雨丝丝欲网春，落花狼藉近黄昏。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>车尘不到张罗地，宿鸟声中自掩门。</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】饮酒晋.陶渊明结庐在人境，而无车马喧。问君何能尔？心远地自偏。采菊东篱下，悠然见南山。山气日夕佳，飞鸟相与还。此中有真意，欲辨已忘言。【乙】春日即事宋.李弥逊小雨丝丝欲网春，落花狼藉近黄昏。车尘不到张罗地，宿鸟声中自掩门。", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a6c85e-64dc-437f-ac5c-050ea3749632@2.pkg/item.json?v=1751872099965", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《饮酒》前两句以平易的语言直接道出作者对幽美平静的田园的喜爱，对车马喧嚣的官场的厌倦。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《春日即事》第三句是诗意之转，诗人所见到的是车水马龙的扬尘之景，而自己的门前却是可以&ldquo;张罗&rdquo;捕鸟,不禁感慨万千。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《饮酒》中&ldquo;见&rdquo;写出了诗人看到南山美景时的随意与自然，体现了作者心灵的自由和惬意；《春日即事》用&ldquo;网&rdquo;字，突出诗人要挣脱春天,躲避春天的心情。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《饮酒》以情为主，融情入景，写出了诗人归隐田园后生活悠闲自得的心境；《春日即事》表达了作者政治上失意后的寂寞以及对世态炎凉的无奈与感叹。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​饮酒</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​晋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>陶渊明</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>结庐在人境，而无车马喧。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>问君何能尔？心远地自偏。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>采菊东篱下，悠然见南山。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>山气日夕佳，飞鸟相与还。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>此中有真意，欲辨已忘言。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​​春日即事</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>宋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>​李弥逊</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>小雨丝丝欲网春，落花狼藉近黄昏。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>车尘不到张罗地，宿鸟声中自掩门。</span></p>\n</div>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "d0a6c85e-64dc-437f-ac5c-050ea3749632", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】饮酒晋.陶渊明结庐在人境，而无车马喧。问君何能尔？心远地自偏。采菊东篱下，悠然见南山。山气日夕佳，飞鸟相与还。此中有真意，欲辨已忘言。【乙】春日即事宋.李弥逊小雨丝丝欲网春，落花狼藉近黄昏。车尘不到张罗地，宿鸟声中自掩门。"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​饮酒</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​晋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>陶渊明</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>结庐在人境，而无车马喧。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>问君何能尔？心远地自偏。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>采菊东篱下，悠然见南山。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>山气日夕佳，飞鸟相与还。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>此中有真意，欲辨已忘言。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: cen